Articles.Content:
great work. i really like the keep-it-simple-stupid principle behind SMU (simple modulemanager adjUstments)--i hope it catches on!<br>
<br>
here&#39;s a stock 3m procedural LFO tank:<br>
<br>
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/wYd7HU3.jpg[/IMG]<br>
<br>
and the same tank with SMURFF:<br>
<br>
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/GUS7iV6.jpg[/IMG]<br>
<br>
<br>
fix:<br>
<br>
[CODE]@PART<br>
[*]:HAS[@MODULE[TankContentSwitcher]]:FOR[SMURFF]{<br>
@MODULE[TankContentSwitcher]<br>
{<br>
@TANK_TYPE_OPTION[Mixed,LiquidFuel,Oxidizer,RCS]<br>
{<br>
@dryDensity /= 4<br>
@RESOURCE[LiquidFuel]<br>
{<br>
@unitsPerT *= 4<br>
}<br>
@RESOURCE[Oxidizer]<br>
{<br>
@unitsPerT *= 4<br>
}<br>
@RESOURCE[Monopropellant]<br>
{<br>
@unitsPerT *= 4<br>
}<br>
}<br>
@TANK_TYPE_OPTION[XenonGas]<br>
{<br>
@dryDensity /= 7<br>
@RESOURCE[XenonGas]<br>
{<br>
@unitsPerT *= 7<br>
}<br>
}<br>
@TANK_TYPE_OPTION[SolidFuel]<br>
{<br>
@dryDensity *= 0.6<br>
@RESOURCE[solidFuel]<br>
{<br>
@unitsPerT /= 0.6<br>
}<br>
}<br>
}<br>
<br>
%MODULE[ModuleSMURFF]{ }<br>
}[/CODE]<br>
<br>
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/7gY6kO8.jpg[/IMG]<br>
<br>
enjoy! :D<br>
